\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-gold\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-charcoal/60\">Invitations to member-only events</span></li></ul><a href=\"mailto:Art@ArtDecoPB.org?subject=Membership: Individual\" class=\"w-full flex items-center justify-center gap-2 py-3 rounded-full text-sm font-medium tracking-wider uppercase transition-colors bg-charcoal text-cream hover:bg-gold hover:text-charcoal\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-mail\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m22 7-8.991 5.727a2 2 0 0 1-2.009 0L2 7\"></path><rect x=\"2\" y=\"4\" width=\"20\" height=\"16\" rx=\"2\"></rect></svg>Join Now</a></div><div class=\"relative rounded-2xl p-8 bg-white\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)\"><h3 class=\"font-display text-xl mb-1 text-charcoal\">Family</h3><div class=\"flex items-baseline gap-1 mb-6\"><span class=\"text-3xl font-display text-charcoal\">$<!-- -->50</span><span class=\"text-sm text-charcoal/50\">/year</span></div><ul class=\"space-y-3 mb-8\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check shrink-0 mt-0.5 text-gold\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20 6 9 17l-5-5\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-charcoal/60\">All Individual benefits</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2 text-sm\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-check 